thread.title: Republican candidate Fiorina raised $6.8 million in third quarter: campaign
thread.title_full: Republican candidate Fiorina raised $6.8 million in third quarter: campaign | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Republican candidate Fiorina raised $6.8 million in third quarter: campaign
text:
WASHINGTON U.S. Republican presidential candidate Carly Fiorina raised $6.8 million since July, the campaign said on Wednesday, a spike fueled by two standout debate performances that skyrocketed the former business executive to the top tier of Republican 2016 White House hopefuls.
Fiorina spent $2.2 million and had $5.5 million in cash remaining going into the last three months of the year, her campaign spokeswoman, Sarah Isgur Flores, tweeted.
(Reporting by Washington Speed Team)
